([ "Account":"ezralee", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! PAINTING ! painting of a still life with fruit. A play of contrasts and highly saturated colors, this still life painting predominantly features a lush red pomegranate at the center of the canvas. The halved fruit is set at an angle atop various other fruits in muted shades of dark plum, rich burgundy, and pale olive green, the resulting contrast calling attention to the bright red seeds of the pomegranate. A beam of hazy light crosses diagonally across the canvas to further illuminate the central focus, the ray glinting off the metallic surface of the ornately detailed dagger that pierces the subject of the piece. The steel poniard features a Celtic knotwork design beset with minute smoky grey gemstones, each one delicately accented with small highlights that mirror the glint of light off the bright red seeds of the fruit within which the razor-sharp blade is situated. The background is otherwise dark by comparison, the only other vibrant accent found in the singular letter E tucked neatly in the lower left-hand corner of the canvas. (\<[IronClaw:Props:Artist:Canvas]#309260\>)", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:to:topsy", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:el:elle", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Southeast:PaintShop:Main", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Topsy (Apr 26 11:18): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1619450322", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1619450322", "TimeClosed":"1619450322", "TimeFiled":"1619401614" ])

([ "Account":"ezralee", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! PAINTING ! painting of a glowing lamp within a niche. \\r\\nEvery inch of the canvas is covered in dark, heavily textured paint save for the beacon-light bright golden aura of the lamp placed at the center of the lower half of the painting. The edges of the canvas where they wrap around the braces have been painted in a trompe loeil stone tile texture that frames the center focus and gives a realistic vision of a three-dimensional stone niche, the perspective narrowing as the leading lines fade into the background. Each piece of stonework is stippled and textured with thickly applied paint that mirrors the coarseness of natural stone, this texture in stark contrast to the smoothness with which the glowing aura of light from within the lamp is applied. Nearly starlight white at its centermost point, the flame of the lamp infuses the squared recesses of the niche with soft rays of light, the milky glass of the lamps shade appearing as though it is glowing in contrast to the darkness of the frame and the diffused lighting of the radiating aura. The painting is noticeably lacking a signature and the colors are softly blended and incredibly lifelike to give added weight to the simple study of the way the light plays within the stone niche, every highlight and shadow painstakingly teased into life by multiple layers of paint and minute, seamlessly blended brushstrokes. \\r\\n (\<[IronClaw:Props:Artist:Canvas]#111211\>)", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:kj:kjell", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:el:elle", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Southeast:PaintShop:Main", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Kjell (May 2 10:30): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1619965830", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1619965830", "TimeClosed":"1619965830", "TimeFiled":"1619754653" ])

([ "Account":"ezralee", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! DRAWING ! drawing of a man in the moonlight. \\r\\nAngled to the left with his weight propped on one hand, this broad-shouldered figure is sketched with a heavy hand in charcoal, the contrast between dark and light stark in the diffused lighting of the nighttime scene. The background is shaded nearly black in entirety, against which the bright white of the drape of the shirt appears to almost glow by comparison. The fabric hugs the curvature of broad shoulders and muscular arms in intricately detailed folds accented by soft shading to lend even more realism to the anatomy of the form beneath. The most highly detailed part of the drawing is the face of the subject. A soft rim light hugs the smooth curve of the cheek and brow, accentuating the wide nose and full lips before it is lost to the facial hair that covers the pointed jaw in a lush beard. Most striking of all are the eyes, slivered catchlights of bright white against a grey backdrop, the solemn gaze turned fractionally away from the viewer in what appears to be deep thought. A hint of a smile crinkles the corner, the expression subtle as it just barely kisses the right-hand side of the lips. The relaxed tilt of the head displays the ornate pattern of folds and creases in the headscarf that coils around the hair, each inch of the fabric teased into dimensionality by a similarly soft play of shadow and light. (\<[IronClaw:Props:Artist:Canvas]#104082\>)", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:kj:kjell", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:el:elle", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Palace:ItalianEstate:FirstFloor:YardNorth", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Kjell (May 9 12:32): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1620577959", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1620577959", "TimeClosed":"1620577959", "TimeFiled":"1620005204" ])

([ "Account":"ezralee", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! PAINTING ! painting of Hylas and the Naiads. Covering the canvas is a lushly textured array of minute brushstrokes detailing a male youth kneeling at the edge of a pond. His face is turned from the viewer, but the lanky form is highlighted in crisp detail by a ray of sunlight streaming from the upper right-hand corner. The taut musculature of his shoulders and back sweeps in a convex curve before it is obscured from view by a swath of dark blue fabric wrapped in folds around the waist. His hand is outstretched over the water, his fingers clasped tight in the grip of a nude female form standing in the waist-deep water of the lily pad laden pond. Corruscating auburn locks float atop the water around her hips, the coquettish expression of her face mirrored in the six other feminine forms that stand arranged behind her in the water. Each of these Naiads has similar fine features, but their hair is a rainbow of hues from jet black to pale blonde, the tresses clinging damply to the swell of their breasts to provide just a bare essence of modesty to the image. The background of the image is loosely detailed, the foliage dark and shadowed in contrast to the paleness of the skin of the subjects. Tucked in the lower left-hand corner, the letter E in crimson paint serves as the artist's signature. (\<[IronClaw:Props:Artist:Canvas]#122074\>)", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:kj:kjell", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:el:elle", "Environment":"[Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Palace:ItalianEstate:SecondFloor:Virtual:NobleSittingRoom]#209539", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Kjell (May 9 12:32): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1620577959", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1620577959", "TimeClosed":"1620577959", "TimeFiled":"1620522081" ])

([ "Account":"lidiab", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! SCULPTURE ! sculpture of Dionysus and Ariadne. This pristine white limestone sculpture represents the divine couple of Dionysus and Ariadne in life-size detail. Ariadne is seated upon Dionysus' lap, her arms outstretched overhead as she reclines against the support of her lover's left arm, her hair hanging down in coruscating tendrils rendered in the same minute detail that is displayed in the expression on her face, eyes crinkled by the silent laugh that parts her lips as she tosses her head back in apparent revelry. Her torso is bare, a simple swath of cloth wrapped around her hips and falling in flowing folds over her legs as well as those of her lover. Dionysus' expression is a mirror to his lover's; creased eyes honed in adoration upon the ecstatic expression of the woman seated upon his lap as he holds a wine glass aloft over her bare torso. The god of wine tilts the glass, a rivulet of the liquid within painstakingly carved into the immalleable stone in lifelike realism as it flows from the lip of the glass to land squarely on the hollow of the woman's chest before running down the smooth expanse of her stomach. The velveteen smoothness of skin is complemented by the seamless texture of the folds of fabric that pool at the feet of the two lovers, each inch of the stone chiseled and polished smooth to convey the lifelike quality of the figures.\\r\\n (\<[IronClaw:Props:Misc:Decorations:Statue]#292230\>)", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:kj:kjell", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:po:polgara", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Northeast:Stonemason:Main", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Kjell (May 9 12:32): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1620577960", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1620577959", "TimeClosed":"1620577960", "TimeFiled":"1620539645" ])

([ "Account":"postalpoppy", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! PAINTING ! painting of a collection of rambunctious satyrs. Colors of deep sanguine and velvety amethyst splash over the majority of this painting. Five mischievous looking satyrs dance their delicate hooves over countless dark grapes and the lush nectar that oozes from them. Two similar looking fawn colored satyrs frame the sides of this painting. Their sturdy, curling horns and childlike faces are angled with joy towards the sunset tinted sky. Pan flutes protrude from their pursed lips, their cheeks puffed up with air blow into them boisterously. In the center, a satyr with silver hair and matching fur blows his flute upwards, a fountain of wine pouring outward from it and splashing the head of his nearby friend. The companion's face is frozen in an eternal chuckle as he is showered with the juice. He lays in the grapes, but not seemingly on purpose. It's as if he laughed so hard he fell over. His fingers are haphazardly curled around a silver goblet and an equally dark liquid spills outward in his clumsiness. In the distant corner of this scene, a reddish-colored satyr with a pointed beard gazes with a look of desire reflected in his eyes at something outside of the painting. (\<[IronClaw:Props:Artist:Canvas]#60195\>)", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:kj:kjell", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:lo:lorna", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Southeast:PaintShop:Main", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Kjell (Jun 24 14:43): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1624560186", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1624560186", "TimeClosed":"1624560186", "TimeFiled":"1624498019" ])

([ "Account":"ezralee", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! DRAWING ! drawing of a tall comedy masked man. \\r\\nVibrant colors and heavy shading cover the surface of the page in a representation of a tall man in a comedy mask. At first glance, he appears austerely dressed in midnight black garb, the slashed-sleeved doublet and collared cape stark in contrast to the more vibrant aspects of the costume. His left hand holds the vibrant yellow mask to his face, the deep ebony skin and tight coils of jet black hair contrasting the vivid color. Similarly ostentatious, the bright yellow doublet hose are held in place by cross-laced tie garters in midnight black, the feet spread shoulder-width apart and the free hand held aloft as if gesticulating wildly. Adding to the contrast with the vivid yellow colors, the background is a muted array of murky green foliage and dark shadowing to call more attention to the subject at the center of the piece. Signed with a tiny flourish at the bottom right corner, the name Dalena can be seen in black ink. \\r\\n (\<[IronClaw:Props:Artist:Canvas]#187917\>)", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:kj:kjell", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:el:elle", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Southeast:PaintShop:Main", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Kjell (Jul 2 10:49): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1625237386", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1625237386", "TimeClosed":"1625237386", "TimeFiled":"1624583449" ])

([ "Account":"ezralee", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! DRAWING ! drawing of a large man in a tuatara mask. \\r\\nVibrant colors and heavy shading cover the surface of the page in a representation of a large man in a tuatara mask. The lush, verdant backdrop of foliage and flowers seems comically oversized when compared to the figure at the center of the page, intentionally drawn to sell the scale of a lizard in its natural habitat. A first glance the outfit seems reserved and traditional, but the contrasting red hue of the velvet vest and the minuscule matching fez hat perched upon the man's short wavy copper hair complements the playful aspects of the ensemble. The warm tones of the clothing accentuate the bronze complexion seen in the figure's hands where he holds the mask to his face, the crouched posture exaggerated to accent the reptilian theme. Signed with a tiny flourish at the bottom right corner, the name Dalena can be seen in black ink. \\r\\n (\<[IronClaw:Props:Artist:Canvas]#187394\>)", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:kj:kjell", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:el:elle", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Southeast:PaintShop:Main", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Kjell (Jul 2 10:49): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1625237386", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1625237386", "TimeClosed":"1625237386", "TimeFiled":"1624584236" ])

DRAWING ! drawing of a lithesome woman in a lioness mask. \\r\\nVibrant colors and heavy shading cover the surface of the page in a representation of a lithesome woman in a lioness mask. Her lustrous red hair is piled high on her head in a grid braid, the color masked by the lace veil worn over it and complemented by the stark contrast of blood-red and glossy garnet accents. The snowdrop white charmeuse dress accentuates the alabaster skin tone, lace trim at the cuffs and hems stark in contrast to the blood-red gloves. ([ "Account":"postalpoppy", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! PAINTING ! painting of a collection of rambunctious satyrs. Colors of deep sanguine and velvety amethyst splash over the majority of this painting. Five mischievous looking satyrs dance their delicate hooves over countless dark grapes and the lush nectar that oozes from them. Two similar looking fawn colored satyrs frame the sides of this painting. Their sturdy, curling horns and childlike faces are angled with joy towards the sunset tinted sky. Pan flutes protrude from their pursed lips, their cheeks puffed up with air blow into them boisterously. In the center, a satyr with silver hair and matching fur blows his flute upwards, a fountain of wine pouring outward from it and splashing the head of his nearby friend. The companion's face is frozen in an eternal chuckle as he is showered with the juice. He lays in the grapes, but not seemingly on purpose. It's as if he laughed so hard he fell over. His fingers are haphazardly curled around a silver goblet and an equally dark liquid spills outward in his clumsiness. In the distant corner of this scene, a reddish-colored satyr with a pointed beard gazes with a look of desire reflected in his eyes at something outside of the painting. In the bottom right corner of this painting are the letters LF with the date 1601 underneath. (\<[IronClaw:Props:Artist:Canvas]#279481\>)", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:kj:kjell", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:lo:lorna", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Southeast:PaintShop:Main", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Kjell (Jul 2 10:50): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1625237425", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1625237424", "TimeClosed":"1625237425", "TimeFiled":"1624745996" ])

PAINTING ! painting of the muse Erato. \\r\\nCovering the entirety of the canvas is a lush textured array of brushstrokes, the pale colors muted and soft in tone. Prominent at the center is the figure of a woman in the nude, her petite form reclined on an ivory upholstered chaise lounge that complements the creamy olive color of her skin. Ringlets of dark brown hair cascade over the bosom, the spiraled tresses offering just an essence of modesty in conjunction with the draping folds of a pale blue swath of fabric lying over her hips. A lyre lies abandoned on the floor beside her amid a tumble of pastel pink rose petals, the bloom from which they have been plucked held aloft in the hands of the subject of the painting. Her expression is serene and almost contemplative as she stares at the rose blossom, but the tease of a smile curves the corners of her mouth in contrast to the serenity of the image. The background of the image is darker in a wash of creams and pale greys, numerous plumed quills and scrolls arranged on shelves filling the space with texture and color that seems hazy when compared to the crisp details of the prone form on the chaise at the foreground. Tucked in the contours of the vignetted darkness of the left-hand corner, the name Dalena can just barely be seen among the brushstrokes. \\r\\n (\<[IronClaw:Props:Artist:Canvas]#199153\>)", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:to:topsy", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:el:elle", "Environment":"[Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Palace:ItalianEstate:SecondFloor:Virtual:NobleSittingRoom]#53966", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Topsy (Nov 15 09:50): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1636987842", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1636987842", "TimeClosed":"1636987842", "TimeFiled":"1631770852" ])
